column2: IDEA-139310: Find Usages reports source code usages first

column3:
This builds upon 327c0fa and does what the issue asks for and people require: source code usages
(static or "dynamic") first, non-code usages (documentation) second, and generated code last..
No CLA necessary. If you agree, please apply the change in your name.

Unfortunately, it is necessary. Could you please download the PDF from http://www.jetbrains.org/display/IJOS/Contributor+Agreement and then print it out, sign (mention you github account name there), scan and email to contribute@jetbrains.com?
No problem! Anything to facilitate seeing this in the next release.

Merged manually. The fix will be included into the next IDEA 16 EAP build.
Thank you for the contribution!
